Gallery3 Contrib

These are unofficial modules, themes and utilities for Gallery 3
created by the Gallery community.  Many of them add considerable value
to your Gallery 3 install, but they come with no official support from
the core Gallery team.

To discuss anything you find here, please refer to the Gallery Google forum:

  https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/gallery-3-users


Due to merging a 3rd party pull request that contained a password, this repository had it's history rewritten to erase the credentials. The commit history will be different from the original fork.
